Muffin Break Logo Muffin Break is a franchise business of Foodco which operates small bakery cafe coffee shops throughout Australia, New Zealand, and the UK. As of 2013, Muffin Break had 275 stores worldwide: 190 in Australia, 37 in New Zealand and 46 in the United Kingdom. Muffin Break is the sister company of Jamaica Blue, which is also a franchise of Foodco. Source
